<p class="">What has that to do with the Working Party Report?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-50c05f78-c71f-4158-93d4-f6642cc4df27" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
