<p class=""><em>indicated assent</em>.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a65ba588-3c0b-4af8-9ad9-4a0fe610d50b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
