        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">There is plenty of time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c7b041d9-4a83-4345-922c-beeb21f318db" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
