    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">But the hon. Member will agree that there was no general impression of that kind from this side of the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-67e55aa9-9703-4c5d-875a-bbe7dbcb9e62" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-22/debates/b01c00ad-e554-4179-be2a-c94c2a40df9d/BuildingIndustry#contribution-67e55aa9-9703-4c5d-875a-bbe7dbcb9e62">
