<p class="">But are they not a different type of house?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af8d05ce-679b-4c40-a99e-1de2bde8fa39" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
