<p class="">The right hon. Lady is beginning again.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2e23a64a-ef9d-4886-bb3f-c053604e70e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
