                Mr. Osborne
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-473bb625-a8bf-4517-9648-6f5682c99d93" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
