<p class="">We should like to know from the Leader of the Opposition—[HON. MEMBERS: "Where is the Prime Minister?"] I should like to ask the right hon. Gentleman a question which is one of very great importance to us on this side of the House and, I am sure, to hon. Gentlemen opposite. We should like to know whether it is now the declared policy of the Opposition to leave entirely to the local authorities the decision of determining how many licences are to be given.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
