liams, Sir H. G. (Croydon, E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lambert, Hon. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Price, H. A. (Lewisham, W.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wills, G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lancaster, Col. C. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Prior-Palmer, Brig. O.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilson, G. (Truro)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Langford-Holt, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Profumo, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterton, Rt. Hon Earl</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Law, Rt. Hon. R. K.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Raikes, H. V.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wood, Hon. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Leather, E. H. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rayner, Brig. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>York, C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Legge-Bourke, Maj. E. A. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Redmayne, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Young, Sir A. S. L. (Partick)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lennox-Boyd, A. T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Remnant, Hon. P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lindsay, Martin</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Renton, D. L. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></p><p class="Division">  <b>TELLERS FOR THE AYES:</b></p><p class="Division"> </td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Linstead, H. N</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Roberts, H. (Wandsworth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>